solution:
载流子浓度  
\[
\begin{aligned}
& R_{\mathrm{H}} = -\frac{1}{n e} \\
& n = -\frac{1}{R_{\mathrm{H}} e} = \frac{1}{1.28 \times 10^{-5} \times 1.6 \times 10^{-19}} = 4.88 \times 10^{23} \, \text{m}^{-3}
\end{aligned}
\]

经过 \(1/4\) 波片后，椭圆偏振光变为线偏振光。因为

\[
\sqrt{I_{2} / I_{3}} = \tan 60^{\circ} = \sqrt{3}
\]

所以

\[
\begin{aligned}
& I_{2} = 3 I_{3}, \\
& I_{3} = \frac{1}{6} I_{0}, \quad I_{1} = \frac{1}{2} I_{0}, \quad I_{2} = \frac{1}{2} I_{0}
\end{aligned}
\]

所以此光的非偏振部分的比例为 \(\frac{I_{1}}{I_{0}} = 50\%\)，椭圆长轴在垂直方向，短轴在水平方向，沿长轴和短轴的相对强度比是 \(I_{2} / I_{3} = 3\).

由于样品足够厚，同时又是恒定表面源条件，解扩散方程得

\[
\Delta p(x)=(\Delta p)_{0} \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{x}{L_{\mathrm{p}}}}
\]

表面注入电流 \(j_{0}=e(\Delta p)_{0} \frac{D_{\mathrm{p}}}{L_{\mathrm{p}}}\)，式中

\[
\begin{gathered}
D_{\mathrm{p}}=\frac{k_{\mathrm{B}} T}{e} \mu_{\mathrm{p}}=0.026 \times 5 \times 10^{2}=13 \mathrm{~cm}^{2} / \mathrm{s} \\
L_{\mathrm{p}}=\sqrt{D_{\mathrm{p}} \tau_{\mathrm{p}}}=\left(13 \times 5 \times 10^{-6}\right)^{\frac{1}{2}}=8.06 \times 10^{-3} \mathrm{~cm}
\end{gathered}
\]

代入 \(D_{\mathrm{p}}, L_{\mathrm{p}}\) 的数值，计算

\[
j_{0}=e(\Delta p)_{0} \frac{D_{\mathrm{p}}}{L_{\mathrm{p}}}=1.6 \times 10^{-19} \times 1 \times 10^{13} \times \frac{13}{8.06 \times 10^{-3}}=2.58 \times 10^{-3} \mathrm{~A} / \mathrm{cm}^{2}
\]

\(B=0\) 时，

\[
n_{\mathrm{r}}^{2}=1-\frac{4 \pi N e^{2} / m}{\omega^{2}}=1-\frac{\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}
\]

即

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \frac{c^{2} k^{2}}{\omega^{2}}=1-\frac{\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}}{\omega^{2}} \\
& \omega^{2}=\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}+c^{2} k^{2}
\end{aligned}
\]

其中，\(\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}=\frac{4 \pi N e^{2}}{m}\)，故相速度

\[
v_{\mathrm{p}}=\frac{\omega}{k}=\frac{c}{\sqrt{1-\frac{\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}}}=\frac{c}{n}
\]

这里的平均自由程是指中子从产生到衰变这段时间内所通过的路程。中子的衰变时间为 1000 秒，它的能量远小于其静止能量，可用非相对论近似，中子的速度为  

\[
\begin{aligned}
& v=\sqrt{\frac{2 E}{m}}=\sqrt{\frac{2 \times 5 \times 10^{-6}}{939.6}} \times 3 \times 10^{8}=1 \times 10^{4} \mathrm{~m} / \mathrm{s} \\
& s=v t=10^{4} \mathrm{~km}
\end{aligned}
\]

由此我们知 e) 是所选的答案。

problem:
Consider a non-degenerate doped semiconductor where the carrier generation transitions from impurity ionization to intrinsic excitation with increasing temperature. Using phosphorus in silicon as an example (with a phosphorus ionization energy in silicon, \(E_{I}=0.045 \ \text{eV}\)), calculate the temperature at the onset of saturation ionization and the onset of intrinsic excitation when the phosphorus impurity concentration is \(10^{17} \ \text{cm}^{-3}\).

\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{ccc}
\hline
浓度 \(/\left(\mathrm{cm}^{-3}\right)\) & \(T_{1} / \mathrm{K}\) & \(T_{2} / \mathrm{K}\) \\
\hline
\(1 \times 10^{17}\) & 281 & 761 \\
\(1 \times 10^{14}\) & 77 & 461 \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
\end{center}

solution:
\[
\begin{aligned}
I & =\int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}}-\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}}+\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}} \\
& =\frac{1}{2} \int_{-\infty}^{0} \frac{\mathrm{~d} x}{4+x^{4}}+\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}}=\frac{1}{2} \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}}
\end{aligned}
\]

由 \(x^{4}+4=0\) 得奇点为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \left\{\begin{array}{l}
x_{1}=1+\mathrm{i} \\
x_{2}=-1+\mathrm{i} \\
x_{3}=-1-\mathrm{i} \\
x_{4}=1-\mathrm{i}
\end{array}\right. \\
& I=\frac{1}{2} \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \frac{\mathrm{d} x}{4+x^{4}}=\frac{1}{2} 2 \pi \mathrm{i}\left[\operatorname{Re}\left(x_{1}\right)+\operatorname{Re}\left(x_{2}\right)\right] \\
& =\pi \mathrm{i}\left[\frac{1}{\left(x_{1}-x_{2}\right)\left(x_{1}-x_{3}\right)\left(x_{1}-x_{4}\right)}+\frac{1}{\left(x_{2}-x_{1}\right)\left(x_{2}-x_{3}\right)\left(x_{2}-x_{4}\right)}\right] \\
& =\pi \mathrm{i}\left[\frac{1}{2(2+2 \mathrm{i})(+2 \mathrm{i})}-\frac{1}{2(+2 \mathrm{i})(-2+2 \mathrm{i})}\right]=\pi \mathrm{i} \frac{1}{8 \mathrm{i}}=\frac{\pi}{8}
\end{aligned}
\]

problem:
Consider a non-degenerate doped semiconductor where the carrier generation transitions from impurity ionization to intrinsic excitation with increasing temperature. Using phosphorus in silicon as an example (with a phosphorus ionization energy in silicon, \(E_{I}=0.045 \ \text{eV}\)), calculate the temperature at the onset of intrinsic excitation when the phosphorus impurity concentration is \(10^{14} \ \text{cm}^{-3}\).

\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{ccc}
\hline
浓度 \(/\left(\mathrm{cm}^{-3}\right)\) & \(T_{1} / \mathrm{K}\) & \(T_{2} / \mathrm{K}\) \\
\hline
\(1 \times 10^{17}\) & 281 & 761 \\
\(1 \times 10^{14}\) & 77 & 461 \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
\end{center}

solution:
对于振子系统来说，每一振子的比热为

\[
\begin{aligned}
c_{\mathrm{CSM}} & =\frac{\partial \overline{\mathcal{E}}}{\partial T}=3 k \\
c_{\mathrm{QSM}} & =\frac{\partial \bar{\varepsilon}}{\partial T}=\frac{3 \hbar \omega_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\beta \hbar \omega_{0}} \left(\frac{\hbar \omega_{0}}{k T}\right)^2 }{\left(\mathrm{e}^{\beta \hbar \omega_{0}}-1\right)^{2}}
\end{aligned}
\]

导带电子有效质量

\[
m_{\mathrm{n}}^{*}=\frac{h^{2}}{\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} E_{C}}{\mathrm{~d} k^{2}}}
\]

由题意

\[
\begin{gathered}
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} E_{C}}{\mathrm{~d} k^{2}}=\frac{2 h^{2}}{3 m_{0}}+\frac{2 h^{2}}{m_{0}}=\frac{8 h^{2}}{3 m_{0}} \\
m_{\mathrm{n}}^{*}=\frac{3 m_{0}}{8}=\frac{3 \times 9.1 \times 10^{-31}}{8}=3.41 \times 10^{-31} \, \mathrm{kg} = 0.375 m_{0}
\end{gathered}
\]

